data.description: Discover timeless elegance in this charming 2-story brick home nestled on 7.88 acres of Southern allure. Perfect for entertaining and family gatherings, its spacious yard offers a playground for kids' laughter and games. Step into a home featuring a formal dining room, a cozy family room/den, a sunlit office/study, and a master bedroom and bath that exude luxury. Radiating old-style Southern charm, this residence is poised to become the heart of a new family's cherished memories. Schedule a showing today to make this house your home.
